    <div class="alpheios-lex-entry" lemma-id="n6912" body-key="α">
          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ὁρμάω</span></b>  (<span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ὁρμή</span>), aor. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ὥρμησα</span>, mid.
          ipf. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ὡρμᾶτο</span>, aor. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ὡρμήσατο</span>, subj. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ὁρμήσωνται</span>, pass. aor. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ὡρμήθην,
            ὁρμηθήτην</span>: I. act., <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">set in motion, impel,
            move;</span>
          <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">πόλεμον, τινὰ ἐς πόλεμον, ς 376</span>, <i><span class="en">Il. 6.338</span></i>; pass. (met.), <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ὁρμηθεὶς θεοῦ</span>, ‘inspired of heaven,’ <i><span class="en">Od. 8.499</span></i>; intrans., <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">start,
            rush;</span>
          <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">τινός</span>, ‘at one,’ <i><span class="en">Il. 4.335</span></i>; w. inf., <i><span class="en">Il. 21.265</span></i> (cf. <i><span class="en">Il. 22.194</span></i>), <i><span class="en">Il. 13.64</span></i>.—II.
          mid., <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">be moved, set out, start, rush</span>, esp. in hostile
          sense, <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">charge upon;</span>
          <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἔγχεϊ, ξιφέεσσι,</span>
          <i><span class="en">Il. 5.855</span></i>, <i><span class="en">Il. 17.530</span></i>; <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc"> τινός</span>, ‘at
          one,’ <i><span class="en">Il. 14.488</span></i>; freq. w. inf., and
          met., <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἦτορ ὡρμᾶτο πολεμίζειν</span>, <i><span class="en">Il. 21.572</span></i>.</div> <div class="alpheios-lex-footnotes en"> </div>
